narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I thought that ITAL 130 was really fun. We saw some great films and it really helped solidify the use of certain tenses, such as the subjunctive. Eleonora is an excellent instructor. She always willing to help and has a great knowledge of the material.
I definitely recommend this class. Definitely take it with Eleonora!
Italian L3 is a recap of L1& L2, with a little more depth, more vocabulary, and more outside sources (like readings, movies, operas, etc.).
